      <scopecontent id="aspace_4367a82ec3734ddb248104913ec669ee">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of files maintained by Robin Winks as a member of the Committee on Canadian Studies, a council of the Yale Center for International and Area Studies.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement id="aspace_eb78cd3a9ed786428cc7046adc800bd2">
