      </arrangement>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_6f98087ceb1590d890925082649a3147">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Some records in this finding aid have been redacted, as they include student names, donor names, and other restricted data. These records will not appear in the published finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
